des: The skill content is in Spanish - La Patrona 1680 AM broadcasts from the Puged Sound region. Station dedicated to entertainment and with the best Mexican music, where the idols of the moment are played. During the week listen to Don Cheto in the morning and the Free Guey Show in the afternoons.
